{"word":"G5091 - τιμάω - timáō - tim-ah'-o - Honour","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">τιμάω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">timáō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tim-ah'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Honour</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கனம் பண்ணு, மதிக்கப்படு, கிரயமாக்கு"},{"paragraph":"1. to estimate, to fix the value"},{"paragraph":"2. to horror to have in honor, to revere, venerate"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5093 - τίμιος - tímios - tim'-ee-os/5093\">G5093</a>; to <i>prize</i>, that is, <i>fix</i> a <i>valuation</i> upon; by implication to <i>revere:</i> - honour, value.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5091/5091\">G5091</a>, <a href=\"#/G5092/5092\">G5092</a>, <a href=\"#/G5093/5093\">G5093</a>, <a href=\"#/G5094/5094\">G5094</a>"}]}